d 'URSTAT': module providing Comprehensive Unified Unit Root & Stationarity Testing
d
d   urstat performs comprehensive unit root and stationarity
d testing on one or more time series	variables simultaneously.
d It produces up to six publication-quality tables and optional   
d high-resolution PNG graphs, consolidating the most widely used
d tests into a single command.	  All tests are applied at Level,
d First Difference, and Second Difference to determine the   
d integration order of each variable. 
d
d KW: unit root tests
d KW: stationarity
d
d Requires: Stata version 14
d
d Distribution-Date: 20260313
d
f urstat.ado
f urstat.sthlp
f urstat_example.do
